Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了莉菲雅后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又得知哥哥艾俄洛斯早已被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚在绝望之中一度身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时 将其救下的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,童虎 撒加和穆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 驰援而至的沙加指出了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亚斯的真实身份就是邪神洛基的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基的目的是吸取黄金圣斗士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使邪恶果实在这片大地上复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　Athena Exclamation\N{\r}凭借着神圣衣的力量 以雅典娜之惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一举消灭了安德烈亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎成功阻止了洛基的完全复活…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我自己得救了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣衣被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的果实之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西就要诞生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想办法阻止它的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果实已从12件黄金圣衣中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及仙宫的大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸取了足以让它成熟的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无人可挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活！仙宫的邪神洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亚斯大人到底在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾正是仙宫之神 洛基！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾将代替奥丁主宰这片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜之惊叹 应该已经阻止了你的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若吾的栖身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那个男人的肉体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也是极难复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾早已另有准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件斗衣 就是吾的另一处栖身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到邪神洛基竟能完全复活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到那朵花蕾绽放之时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之野心便会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你如愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在果实完全成熟之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会打倒你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还有力气战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能独自一人从世界之树中成功逃脱也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你区区一介人类能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况是在这种失去圣衣的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至不可能触碰到吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃抵抗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命被人玩弄于掌中 自己却束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就懊悔着自己的无力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次赴死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金圣衣正在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了如此不成器的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金圣衣竟流下了眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣衣流泪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无稽之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻彻底底的绝望已在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却仍然不愿正视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而沉浸于名为希望的幻想之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还真是可悲的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是艾俄洛斯哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变坚强了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩下孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也坚持战斗至此 干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 从现在起你不再是孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射手座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽失去了圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却被瓦拉哈拉宫的人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Polaris　　　　\N{\r}之后我从北极星的希路达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知了一切的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括安德烈亚斯的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是邪神洛基一事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来希路达已经察觉到吾的真身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北极星的希路达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基 我最初便清楚你的所有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 从封印之中被解放的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依附在宫廷医师安德烈亚斯·里瑟的肉体之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待着在这片大地上完全复活的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 雅典娜与哈迪斯的战火燃起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为这是将地上据为己有的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这座仙宫之中 却有个名为奥丁的眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基你打算利用在冥界牺牲的12名黄金圣斗士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那种被誉为可匹敌太阳的圣衣之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使世界之树的果实 孕育出毁灭性的恐怖力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙宫传说中的究极神器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Gungnir\N{\r}永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 希路达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能够得到永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥丁之流便不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌 艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在永恒之枪诞生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒洛基便可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为区区人类能办到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况是在没有黄金圣衣的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能成什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强弱并不由所穿的圣衣决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将自身蕴藏的小宇宙爆发到何种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此一点才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小宇宙也产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都至少要保护希路达大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希路达大人 这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基所操纵的死者的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英灵战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Paal De Bril\N{\r}北极闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亡者们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们碰希路达大人分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我神斗士格拉尼的西格蒙德还站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的拳中苏醒吧 狮子之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Lightning Plasma\N{\r}等离子光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的拳啊 化为正义之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诛杀邪恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Atomic Thunder Bolt\N{\r}原子雷电光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苟延残喘的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有灵魂的士兵 无论来多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是我们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要掉以轻心 艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果实很快就要成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也差不多该让你们消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类们 消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先暂且退后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的仙宫之神奥丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请倾听我们这些侍奉奥丁的神斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和仙宫子民的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾俄洛斯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算落入敌人的陷阱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论暴露出怎样的丑态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们圣斗士的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都并不是由此决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经 我不惧背负逆贼的污名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便遭到追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要拯救雅典娜的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我心中有唯一的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信念？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也是同样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了正在冥界战斗的年轻圣斗士们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用这新的生命应该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让生命延续到下一个世代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这反应是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.80,remark,NTP,0,0,0,,Draupnir，北欧神话中奥丁拥有的每九天就会自行复制一次的指环或臂环，也被称为“聚金指环”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有着足以封印邪神力量的宝具“德罗普尼尔”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射手座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这德罗普尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定能够再次封印洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说 如果不被德罗普尼尔所认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便无法发挥出它真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德罗普尼尔正和你的小宇宙产生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花就快要开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒之枪就将为吾所有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不会让永恒之枪落入你手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此急于求死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所愿 让你的性命断绝于此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这拳让你回归虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 刚才的力量是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德罗普尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然藏着那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Lightning Plasma\N{\r}等离子光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不被德罗普尼尔直接击中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的区区攻击算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的武器不就白费了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知分寸的愚蠢人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾俄洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们坚持不懈 战斗至此 值得嘉奖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这个庞大的小宇宙是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙宫的伟大神明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是仙宫之神 奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲亚竟然是奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的惊讶也是无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅正是接替希路达大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被授予了奥丁之力的地上代行者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌特迦从很早以前就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亚斯的真实身份是邪神洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 奥丁要在新的地上代行者身上完全觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都必须在洛基眼皮底下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}　　　　　　　　　　　　　Odin Robe\N{\r}将终有一日要派上用场的奥丁斗衣隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌特迦自绝性命化身英灵战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借此将奥丁斗衣隐藏在了自己体内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在根据奥丁神的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被指名选择为守护仙宫的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被奥丁选中？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被选中的并非仙宫中人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你 此事实在令人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 艾欧里亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥丁神会认同你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就说明你毫无疑问是真正的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让永恒之枪在这片大地上复活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 就与这把剑一同战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这道光是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥丁斗衣披挂在了艾欧里亚身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我狮子座的艾欧里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实接收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被托付了奥丁斗衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾欧里亚与邪神洛基展开激战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 圣斗士星矢 黄金魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生！神器永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
